{"type":"message","id":"3c7b8368","parentId":"fa7a6ce3","timestamp":"2026-03-03T12:46:26.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说已经登录了，让我把浏览器设置成默认用网关的浏览器。\n\n首先我需要确认一下用户已经登录成功，然后看看怎么设置默认浏览器。不过\"设置默认浏览器\"这个说法有点模糊——用户可能是想让我以后都用网关浏览器（而不是 Chrome 扩展 relay），或者是想配置什么东西。\n\n让我先重新 snapshot 看看登录后的状态，然后回复用户。\n\n关于\"默认浏览器\"，在 OpenClaw 里，browser 工具可以指定 target 参数：\n- target=\"sandbox\" - 沙箱浏览器\n- target=\"host\" - 主机浏览器（网关）\n- target=\"node\" - 节点浏览器\n\n默认是 host。用户可能是想让我明确用网关浏览器，不要用 Chrome 扩展（profile=\"chrome\"）。\n\n我先看看当前页面状态，然后回复用户。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6d740a494891482e8e290757","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"snapshot","targetId":"B275EEB53107EB30FA87BD07EA5DB797","refs":"aria"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":40478,"output":423,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772541969694}}
